0001-luamem.patch fixes an issue with the 2.5.1 tagged version of Lua's C
sources. It is otherwise unrelated to Rammel's sources, but this patch is not
vendored software so it is in this src subdirectory rather than the vendor
subdirectory.

0002-lua-2.5.1-inout.c.patch fixes another issue with Lua's sources.

Makefile is the former nwconfig.